check_bookmark_type_references.name: check_bookmark_type_references
check_bookmark_type_references.value:
(
        (type = 'movie'::bookmark_type AND movie_id IS NOT NULL AND tv_series_id IS NULL)
        OR
        (type = 'tv_series'::bookmark_type AND tv_series_id IS NOT NULL AND movie_id IS NULL)
      )

check_playlist_description_check.name: check_playlist_description_check
check_playlist_description_check.value:
((description IS NULL) OR ((length(description) >= 1) AND (length(description) <= 300))) AND ((description IS NULL) OR (description !~ '.*
s*
.*'::text)) AND ((description IS NULL) OR (TRIM(BOTH FROM description) <> ''::text))
